<div class="row-fluid border-bottom">
  <h3 class="intro">If you’ve ever dreamed of helping remote communities get equal access to water, compelled to stand up for animal rights, or inspired to share your passion for a sustainable food system with the next generation, the Faculty of Land and Food Systems (LFS) may be the right Faculty for you.
<br>
<br>To learn more about LFS and to see if it's the right fit for you, we invite you to visit beautiful Vancouver and <a href="https://www.landfood.ubc.ca/prospective/lfs-events/#campus">check out a on campus event</a> for prospective students. Our Student Advisors also visit cities to talk about LFS; see if they're coming <a href="https://www.landfood.ubc.ca/prospective/lfs-events/#community">to your community</a>.</h3>
</div>
<div class="row-fluid border-bottom" id="campus">
  <h1>On Campus</h1>
<h3>LFS Fall Preview Day</h3>
<p>Whether you’re in high school and exploring your post-secondary options for the first time, or already in a college/university program and looking for a change, we invite you bring your friends and family to meet with us at our LFS Fall Preview Day.
<p>Join us for LFS Fall Preview Day and you will:
  <ul>
    <li>Find out what makes our Faculty and programs unique</li>
    <li>Learn more about our three <a href="https://www.landfood.ubc.ca/undergraduate/#programs">undergraduate Bachelor of Science degrees</a></li>
    <li>Hear from staff, students, and faculty who will share their passions with you</li>
    <li>Have your questions answered about next steps to submit an application</li></ul>
<p>At Fall Preview Day, there will be designated Student Services staff available to answer your advising and admission related questions. You will learn about some of the many exciting career opportunities available to LFS graduates and have an opportunity to meet with current LFS students who are excited to share their UBC and LFS experiences with you!</p>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, November 24, 2018
<p><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00am to 12:30pm (check-in starts at 9:30am)
<p><strong>Where:</strong> <a href="http://www.maps.ubc.ca/PROD/index_detail.php?show=y,n,n,n,n,y&bldg2Search=n&locat1=449&locat2=">Food, Nutrition and Health Building</a>
<p><strong>Registration:</strong> <a href="https://ubc.ca1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_0Cfy6boe3uwpbdH">click here to RSVP</a>.

</div>
